{"tid":1933073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗男女]一對男女警員於當值期間多次於當值中心內發生性行為，被篤灰後當局訓斥","createTime":"2020-03-19T05:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:34:48.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a06ce65170598c326f162998ed779d8193fa455d","tid":1933073,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日本兵庫縣</span></strong>一對男女警員由去年12月至今年2用期間，於當值期間多次於當值中心內發生性行為，男警員已婚，女警員未婚，被指多次於沒有其他警員當值既當值中心內發生性行為，被篤灰後當局扣減男性警員1/10隻人工一個月，而女警員就被訓斥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN3M4GB0N3LPIHB01P.html?iref=comtop_8_06\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Farticles%2FASN3M4GB0N3LPIHB01P.html%3Firef%3Dcomtop_8_06&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=d7ade236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN3M4GB0N3LPIHB01P.html?iref=comtop_8_06</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兵庫県警尼崎東署の男女2人の警察官が昨年12月～今年2月、夜間勤務中に交番で性行為をしていたとして、同県警が2人を19日付で処分したことが関係者への取材でわかった。ほかの警察官が上司に相談して判明。2人は事実関係を認めているという。<br />\n<br />\n 県警関係者によると、2人は30代の男性巡査部長と、20代の女性巡査。夜間勤務中、他の署員がいない管内の交番休憩室で複数回、性行為をしたという。県警の業務への支障はなかったとされる。<br />\n<br />\n 既婚の男性巡査部長が、部下で独身の女性巡査を誘っていたといい、県警は信用失墜行為として、19日付で男性巡査部長を減給10分の1（1カ月）の懲戒処分に、女性巡査を本部長訓戒にした。"},{"pid":"83ccad3e63d4d2abadb01ff5fed3505bffce61cd","tid":1933073,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"eef49cbb63d3fa3ee281a3dc39b0960d1e31fc95","tid":1933073,"uid":161190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"AV情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a71d073a9c5bdfb623f741f9f0c02a4ffadf9f","tid":1933073,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eef49cbb63d3fa3ee281a3dc39b0960d1e31fc95","tid":1933073,"uid":161190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"AV情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"秘密女搜查官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca1ab9999db11e9577503495c0c7b5030450fa6","tid":1933073,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"訓斥係咪即係屌多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ad8d0cf48ba8e5ffd5919c65ad6233264c82e1","tid":1933073,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"男沙展與女散仔差館扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd97f2a03df96573312b68f3838b3636c8dfac4e","tid":1933073,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca1ab9999db11e9577503495c0c7b5030450fa6","tid":1933073,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"訓斥係咪即係屌多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"訓住斥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7020eb1087fadf860925ad493acfa6dc8524c689","tid":1933073,"uid":124806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"諗返起次前有個日本女警都係做風俗比人捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}